:11715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"有興趣，但寄香港運費點計"},{"pid":"f414b1ef8bdeb48860a5e6f189c8e306bd8d6d68","tid":133862,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hk card俾到錢？</blockquote><br />\n用line pay就用到hk卡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打可唔可以講詳細d?<br />\n要另外充定好似Apple pay咁記左你張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先download line, 開個line id<br />\n跟住download line pay, 然後喺入面link自己信用咭<br />\n之後去zozotown買嘢, 比錢嗰度揀用line pay<br />\n<br />\n跟住會直接彈去line pay叫你㩒密碼確認付款<br />\n直接喺信用咭扣"},{"pid":"b964f2a6dd7ac9105cd97c70a7895f8f41165116","tid":133862,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"樓上咁多位巴打<br />\n我喺寄去集運再船便嚟香港<br />\n你可以分開單寄去自己嘅集運 直寄你屋企<br />\n或者用我嗰間 寄你屋企<br />\n<br />\n因為我買wego啲減價嘢 幾百yen<br />\n好難過5000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋每次都要儲埋一堆<br />\n儲得嚟有啲都比人買哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係方便啲唔夠5000<br />\n又想隨時買 又唔願比運費嘅 (例如我呢啲)<br />\n咁嘅巴/絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實新登記可以free試用兩個月platinum <br />\n(價值月額&yen;500, 即日送貨, 送料無料;<br />\npremium係送料無但唔包即日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n每月1號開始, 月尾申請都當你1個月計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴絲們可以試完再嚟join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔知 如果不停咁用新email呃試用<br />\n會唔會比佢bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 1號會用新地址新email新嘗試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d29dc2b610cf6721e509cbee00644d515b43f2e0","tid":133862,"uid":75419